metadata.description:
This is YOUR key to the Tavern. So make sure you don't lose it.

Tavern Key **HOLDER **Access:

-1 Free NFT a month. Airdropped compliments of the Tavern.

-Exclusive NFT Giveaways

-Top 1/1 Artist Collaboratives

-A collaboration of informed, driven, and passionate artists who just love doing what they do.

-Learn and grow along with us!

-and more!

ATTENTION:

"Trash Fire Tavern: Virtual Interactive Platform"

Using the technology of UnReal Engine, The Tavern is under construction as we speak! This will be an opportunity to interact in a real time virtual environment to develop positive relationships with each other as we all learn and grow together. It's all about doing our best and helping each other along the way.

Because I hate saying Metaverse...

This key gives access to the Grand Opening!! (TBA)

Come join us at the Tavern!  
Be a part of something Monumental.
